<p>'Full of joy!' wrote the 35-year-old Gossip Girl star, who uploaded a photo of her baby bump to Instagram on Wednesday. </p>

<p>In the black-and-white snapshot, Szohr looked to be in the midst of laughter as Richardson gazed down at her burgeoning belly. </p>

<p>Full of joy!</p>

